      "content": "it's more than just being tired though. it feels like a trap. every \"positive\" thing people say about the future feels like a lie or just pure delusion. it feels like we're all just passengers on a sinking ship, and everyone is pretending we're on a cruise. it makes everything i do—every single thing—feel so incredibly pointless. like, what's the point of even being here to witness it?",
